summary: This document is an Indenture dated October 21, 2025, involving Exeter Automobile Receivables Trust 2025-5 (Issuer), Exeter Holdings Trust 2025-5 (Holding Trust), and Citibank, N.A. (Indenture Trustee), outlining the terms for various classes of asset-backed notes. It details the obligations, rights, and responsibilities of the parties, including the payment of principal and interest, events of default, and the roles and duties of the Indenture Trustee.
